DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-04-11T04:30:00&endDate=2026-04-13T01:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nDISTRICT LINE: Saturday 11 and Sunday 12 April\, no service between Embankment / Edgware Road and Ealing Broadway / Kensington (Olympia) / Richmond / Wimbledon. Use MILDMAY LINE services between Gunnersbury\, Kew Gardens and Richmond\, when available. The PICCADILLY LINE will not operate between Hyde Park Corner and Acton Town until 0700 Saturday. Replacement buses operate.
